  "description": "<i>NBA 2K1</i> is the second game in <b>Sega's</b> NBA 2K series of basketball simulation games for the Dreamcast. The graphics from the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/nba-2k\">2K edition</a> have been updated and the team rosters match the official NBA 2000-2001 rosters.<br><br>Besides all the usual modes &amp; coaching options <i>NBA 2K1</i> features several improvements over it's predecessor:<ul><li>New franchise &amp; GM mode.\n<li>Street mode in which you can play, for instance, 2-on-2 and 3-on-3 hoops.\n<li>NBA legends teams, play with some of the best players in NBA history (they wear their authentic vintage jersey's).\n<li>Network mode for Internet-play.\n</ul><br><br><i>NBA 2K1</i> is endorsed by Allen Iverson of the Philadelphia 76'ers.",
